<body>
    <h1>Lasagna</h1>
    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400" alt="Lasagna">
    
    <h2>Description</h2>
    <p>Lasagna is a popular Italian dish made of layers of pasta, meat sauce, and cheese.</p>
    
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Lasagna noodles</li>
        <li>Ground beef</li>
        <li>Ricotta cheese</li>
        <li>Tomato sauce</li>
        <li>Cheddar cheese</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Steps</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).</li>
        <li>Boil the lasagna noodles.</li>
        <li>Cook the ground beef in a pan.</li>
        <li>Assemble the lasagna layers and bake for 45 minutes.</li>
    </ol>
